íŸ@d4d228868a076eb972e1eed61303fd42f6f9ad25986c5b436f483d1e95544697⁄ôTitle: title: plugin
Path: Examples
Content:
Run the 
``nu_plugin_inc``
 plugin from the current directory and install its signatures.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> plugin add nu_plugin_inc


```
Load (or reload) the 
``inc``
 plugin from the plugin registry file and put its

commands in scope. The plugin must already be in the registry file at parse

time.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> plugin use inc


```
List installed plugins
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> plugin list


```
Stop the plugin named 
``inc``
.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> plugin stop inc


```
Remove the installed signatures for the 
``inc``
 plugin.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> plugin rm inc


```
