[link: /commands/docs/plugin_add.md] ``plugin add``
Add a plugin to the plugin registry file.
built-in
[link: /commands/docs/plugin_list.md] ``plugin list``
List loaded and installed plugins.
built-in
[link: /commands/docs/plugin_rm.md] ``plugin rm``
Remove a plugin from the plugin registry file.
built-in
[link: /commands/docs/plugin_stop.md] ``plugin stop``
Stop an installed plugin if it was running.
built-in
[link: /commands/docs/plugin_use.md] ``plugin use``
Load a plugin from the plugin registry file into scope.
keyword
